utdown\n ip address 10.0.0.1/32\n!\ninterface eth1\n no shutdown\n description ce1 -> dut [external]\n ip address 10.1.0.13/30\n!\ndo write\nCONFIG\nvtysh -f /tmp/config\n!\nexit 0\n"
